nnifer%20Lopez%20and%20Ben%20Affleck's%20divorce%20was%20finalized%20by%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20judge%2C%20making%20them%20officially%20single.%20The%20couple%20avoided%20a%20courtroom%20dispute%20through%20mediation.%20Lopez%20has%20removed%20all%20references%20to%20Affleck%20from%20her%20Instagram%20and%20is%20celebrating%20her%20newly%20single%20status.%20She%20is%20also%20celebrating%20her%20twins%E2%80%99%2017th%20birthday%20with%20a%20special%20post%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Attack%20On%20Conductor%20Flared%20Up%20Historic%20Maharashtra-Karnataka%20Border%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBus%20services%20between%20Karnataka%20and%20Maharashtra%20have%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20after%20tensions%20flared%20up%20on%20Friday%20when%20a%20bus%20conductor%20was%20beaten%20up%20in%20Belagavi%20for%20allegedly%20not%20responding%20in%20Marathi.%20In%20a%20retaliatory%20move%2C%20some%20unidentified%20individuals%20attacked%20and%20blackened%20a%20bus%20driver%20of%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(MSRTC)%20in%20Chitradurga%20district%20of%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20have%20led%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20bus%20services%20between%20the%20two%20states.%20Both%20Karnataka%20and%20Maharashtra%20transport%20corporations%20have%20restricted%20their%20operations%2C%20citing%20safety%20concerns%20for%20passengers%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Incident%20In%20Belagavi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20trigger%20for%20the%20recent%20flare-up%20was%20an%20altercation%20in%20Marihal%2C%20a%20locality%20in%20Karnataka's%20Belagavi%20district%2C%20on%20Friday.%20A%20conductor%20of%20a%20Karnataka%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(KSRTC)%20bus%20was%20reportedly%20attacked%20by%20a%20group%20of%20men%20for%20not%20responding%20to%20a%20passenger%20in%20Marathi.%20According%20to%20the%20conductor's%20police%20complaint%2C%20a%20girl%20had%20asked%20for%20a%20ticket%20in%20Marathi.%20When%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20understand%20Marathi%20and%20requested%20her%20to%20speak%20in%20Kannada%2C%20she%20and%20her%20male%20companion%20allegedly%20assaulted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20quickly%20escalated%20when%20a%20larger%20group%20intercepted%20the%20bus%20and%20physically%20assaulted%20the%20conductor.%20The%20police%20have%20arrested%20four%20individuals%20involved%20in%20the%20attack.%20However%2C%20the%20conductor%20was%20also%20booked%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20after%20the%20girl%20filed%20a%20complaint%20alleging%20'indecent%20behaviour'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetaliation%20In%20Chitradurga%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20retaliatory%20act%2C%20a%20bus%20driver%20from%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(MSRTC)%20was%20attacked%20the%20following%20day%20in%20Hiriyur%20Taluk%20of%20Karnataka's%20Chitradurga%20district.%20The%20victim%2C%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav%2C%20was%20blackened%20with%20paint%20by%20unidentified%20individuals.%20Police%20have%20arrested%20several%20individuals%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Maharashtra's%20Transport%20Minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik%20announced%20a%20halt%20to%20MSRTC%20bus%20services%20to%20Karnataka.%20He%20said%20an%20MSRTC%20bus%20travelling%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Mumbai%20was%20attacked%20in%20Chitradurga%20around%209%3A10%20pm%20on%20Friday%20by%20pro-Kannada%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20an%20ultra-luxury%20KSRTC%20bus%20was%20vandalised%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20slogans%20like%20'Jai%20Maharashtra'%2C%20'Marathi'%2C%20and%20'Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena'%20scribbled%20across%20its%20body%20in%20black%20paint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20rising%20hostilities%2C%20Karnataka%20has%20also%20reduced%20its%20bus%20services%20to%20Maharashtra.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20limited%20the%20number%20of%20buses%20going%20to%20Maharashtra%20for%20the%20time%20being%20and%20are%20taking%20all%20precautions%20to%20normalize%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20the%20North%20West%20Karnataka%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20(NWKRTC)%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20our%20Maharashtra%20counterparts%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20resolution%20and%20the%20resumption%20of%20bus%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistoric%20Context%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelagavi%2C%20a%20district%20with%20a%20substantial%20Marathi-speaking%20population%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20historic%20border%20dispute%20between%20the%20two%20states.%20Maharashtra%20has%20repeatedly%20claimed%20Belagavi%20(formerly%20Belgaum)%20and%20several%20other%20villages%20along%20the%20border%2C%20arguing%20that%20they%20were%20wrongly%20assigned%20to%20Karnataka%20in%20India's%20landmark%20act%20to%20redraw%20state%20boundaries%20in%201956%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20Maharashtra%20four%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20firmly%20opposed%20any%20such%20claims.%20To%20reinforce%20its%20position%2C%20it%20has%20constructed%20the%20Suvarna%20Vidhana%20Soudha%20in%20Belagavi%2C%20where%20the%20state%20legislature%20holds%20annual%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201966%2C%20the%20Mahajan%20Commission%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20rejecting%20Maharashtra's%20claims%20over%20Belagavi.%20However%2C%20Maharashtra%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20decision%20and%20took%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202004%2C%20where%20it%20remains%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740295140000%2C%22visua