%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20post%2C%20Agrawal%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20free%20to%20tweet-%20is%20Twitter%20dying%3F%20or%20anything%20else%20about%20Twitter-%20but%20it's%20my%20responsibility%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20it's%20not%20helping%20me%20make%20Twitter%20better%20in%20the%20current%20context.%20Next%20time%20we%20speak%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20provide%20you%20with%20perspective%20on%20the%20level%20of%20internal%20distraction%20and%20how%20it%20is%20hurting%20our%20ability%20to%20do%20work.%20I%20hope%20the%20AMA%20will%20help%20people%20get%20to%20know%20you%2C%20to%20understand%20why%20you%20believe%20in%20Twitter%2C%20and%20to%20trust%20you-%20and%20I'd%20like%20the%20company%20to%20get%20to%20a%20place%20where%20we%20are%20more%20resilient%20and%20don't%20get%20distracted%2C%20but%20we%20aren't%20there%20right%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%2C%20Musk%20had%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20you%20get%20done%20this%20week%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20exchange%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20fallout%20between%20the%20two%2C%20eventually%20led%20to%20Musk%20firing%20Agrawal%20from%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDOGE's%20Notice%20To%20Federal%20Workers%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20The%20Trump%20administration%20sent%20emails%20to%20US%20federal%20government%20employees%20telling%20them%20to%20detail%20their%20work%20accomplishments%20from%20the%20previous%20week%20by%20Monday%20night%20or%20risk%20losing%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emails%20came%20shortly%20after%20Musk%20posted%20on%20the%20social%20media%20site%20X%20that%20not%20responding%20to%20the%20email%20request%20would%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20resignation.%20%26quot%3BAll%20federal%20employees%20will%20shortly%20receive%20an%20email%20requesting%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20got%20done%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFailure%20to%20respond%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20a%20resignation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20issued%20his%20post%20just%20hours%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20posted%20on%20his%20own%20social%20media%20network%2C%20Truth%20Social%2C%20that%20DOGE%20should%20get%20more%20aggressive%20in%20its%20attempts%20to%20downsize%20and%20reshape%20the%202.3%20million-strong%20federal%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20emails%20were%20sent%20to%20employees%20across%20federal%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%2C%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20and%20others%20with%20the%20subject%20line%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20you%20do%20last%20week%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20subject%20line%20harks%20back%20to%20Musk's%20poser%20to%20Agrawal%20three%20years%20ago.%20The%20email%20reportedly%20asks%20employees%20to%20reply%20with%20five%20bullet%20points%20summarizing%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20you%20accomplished%20at%20work%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20copy%20their%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20sent%20from%20a%20human%20resources%20address%20from%20the%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20and%20gives%20employees%20until%2011%3A59%20p.m.%20EST%20on%20Monday%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20what%20legal%20basis%20Musk%20has%20to%20terminate%20federal%20workers%20if%20they%20fail%20to%20respond%20to%20his%20request%20and%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20employees%20who%20cannot%20detail%20confidential%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20federal%20judiciary%20employees%20received%20the%20email%20on%20Saturday%20from%20OPM%2C%20even%20though%20the%20court%20system%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20executive%20branch%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20at%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20also%20rep