ot%3BMud%20They%20Throw%20At%20Us...%26quot%3B%3A%20Giorgia%20Meloni's%20Shoutout%20For%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EItalian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20launched%20a%20scathing%20critique%20of%20what%20she%20describes%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bliberal%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20accusing%20the%20Left%20of%20hypocrisy%20and%20of%20reacting%20with%20%26quot%3Bhysteria%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20conservative%20leaders%20globally.%20Speaking%20via%20video%20link%20at%20the%20Conservative%20Political%20Action%20Conference%20(CPAC)%20in%20Washington%20DC%20on%20Saturday%2C%20PM%20Meloni%20praised%20US%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-usaid-doge-elon-musk-they-take-advantage-of-us-trumps-latest-jab-over-usaid-funds-for-india-7773752%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20while%20attacking%20what%20she%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Belites%26quot%3B%20and%20left-wing%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Meloni%20argued%20that%20liberals%20have%20become%20increasingly%20frustrated%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20right-wing%20leaders%2C%20particularly%20following%20President%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20Tony%20Blair%20created%20the%20global%20leftist%20liberal%20network%20in%20the%2090s%2C%20they%20were%20called%20statesmen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20when%20Trump%2C%20Meloni%2C%20(Javier)%20Milei%2C%20or%20maybe%20(Narendra)%20Modi%20talk%2C%20they%20are%20called%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy.%20This%20is%20the%20Left's%20double%20standard%2C%20but%20we%20are%20used%20to%20it.%20And%20the%20good%20news%20is%20people%20no%20longer%20believe%20in%20their%20lies.%20Despite%20all%20the%20mud%20they%20throw%20at%20us%2C%20citizens%20keep%20voting%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Meloni%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Italian%20leader%20also%20dubbed%20President%20Trump%20as%20a%20steadfast%20leader%20who%20would%20remain%20aligned%20with%20global%20conservatives%20despite%20external%20pressures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Left%20is%20nervous%2C%20and%20with%20Trump's%20victory%2C%20their%20irritation%20has%20turned%20into%20hysteria.%20Not%20only%20because%20conservatives%20are%20winning%2C%20but%20because%20conservatives%20are%20now%20collaborating%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20far-right%20Brothers%20of%20Italy%20party%2C%20PM%20Meloni%20was%20the%20only%20EU%20head%20of%20government%20to%20attend%20President%20Trump's%20inauguration%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Meloni's%20decision%20to%20address%20CPAC%20was%20met%20with%20strong%20opposition%20from%20her%20political%20adversaries%20in%20Rome.%20The%20controversy%20intensified%20after%20Steve%20Bannon%2C%20Trump's%20former%20chief%20strategist%2C%20appeared%20to%20use%20a%20Nazi%20salute%20during%20the%20conference%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20called%20on%20PM%20Meloni%20to%20cancel%20her%20participation%2C%20following%20the%20lead%20of%20Jordan%20Bardella%2C%20leader%20of%20France's%20National%20Rally%20(RN)%20party%2C%20who%20withdrew%20from%20CPAC%20over%20what%20he%20described%20as%20Bannon's%20%26quot%3Bgesture%20alluding%20to%20Nazi%20ideology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElly%20Schlein%2C%20leader%20of%20Italy's%20center-left%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20was%20among%20those%20urging%20PM%20Meloni%20to%20distance%20herself%20from%20the%20event.%20%26quot%3BShe%20should%20have%20the%20decency%20to%20disassociate%20herself%20from%20this%20neo-fascist%20gathering%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Schlein%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20not%20said%20a%20word%20for%20days%20about%20Trump's%20insults%20and%20frontal%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%20She%20is%20unable%20to%20defend%20Italian%