80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1893419979695104283%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20yesterday%20addressed%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20President%20Trump's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20information%20has%20been%20put%20out%20there%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20people%2C%20and%20obviously%2C%20that%20is%20concerning.%20I%20think%2C%20as%20a%20government%2C%20we're%20looking%20into%20it.%20My%20sense%20is%20that%20the%20facts%20will%20come%20out.%20USAID%20was%20allowed%20here%20in%20good%20faith%2C%20to%20do%20good%20faith%20activities%3B%20now%2C%20suggestions%20are%20being%20laid%20out%20from%20America%20that%20there%20are%20activities%20which%20are%20in%20bad%20faith.%20It's%20worrisome%2C%20and%20if%20there's%20something%20to%20it%2C%20then%20the%20country%20should%20know%20who%20the%20people%20are%20involved%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20demanded%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20funds%20received%20in%20India%20from%20developmental%20agencies%20and%20aid%20mechanisms.%20Congress%20also%20sought%20legal%20action%20against%20those%20propagating%20allegations%20of%20foreign%20interference%20in%20Indian%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20responded%20to%20President%20Trump's%20remarks%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BMore%20Indian%20news%20media%20outlets%20have%20fact-checked%20the%20claim%20by%20BJP%20and%20Modi%20government's%20minister%20as%20untrue.%20Funds%20went%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%20not%20India%3B%20although%20India%20received%20USAID%20funds%2C%20it%20was%20not%20for%20increasing%20voter%20turnout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20also%20alleged%20that%20an%20unnamed%20firm%20in%20Bangladesh%20had%20received%20%2429%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGot%20USD%2029%20million.%20They%20got%20a%20check.%20Can%20you%20imagine%3F%20You%20have%20a%20little%20firm%2C%20you%20get%2010%2C000%20here%2C%2010%2C000%20there%2C%20and%20then%20we%20get%2029%20million%20from%20the%20United%20States%20government.%20There%20are%20two%20people%20working%20in%20that%20firm...%20I%20think%20they're%20very%20happy%2C%20they're%20very%20rich.%20They'll%20be%20on%20the%20cover%20of%20a%20very%20good%20business%20magazine%20pretty%20soon%20for%20being%20great%20scammers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20has%20urged%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20%26quot%3Btalk%20to%20his%20friend%26quot%3B%20and%20refute%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20President%20Trump.%20The%20party%20further%20criticised%20the%20Modi%20government's%20approach%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20leveraging%20the%20US%20President's%20claims%20to%20bolster%20conspiracy%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20record%20of%20a%20Consortium%20for%20Elections%20and%20Political%20Process%20Strengthening%20(CEPPS)%20program%20matching%20the%20US%20government's%20description%20in%20India.%20CEPPS%20did%20have%20a%20%2421%20million%20USAID%20contract%2C%20but%20it%20was%20for%20Bangladesh%2C%20not%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khera%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Ajay%20Alok%20dismissed%20Congress's%20statements%20as%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20shown%20that%20the%20government%20got%20%242119%20million%20between%202004-14%20and%20just%201.5%20million%20between%202014-25.%20We%20are%20shutting%20down%20these%20things.%20The%20Indian%20government%20is%20now%20acting%2C%20the%20US%20government%20has%20issued%20a%20list%20of%20who%20has%20got%20the%20money%20from%20where...%20this%20is%20part%20of%20a%20deep%20state.%20The%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20also%20being%20funded%20from%20this%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Alok%20claimed