0car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20then%20went%20to%20a%20police%20station%20but%20later%20mutually%20decided%20not%20to%20take%20any%20further%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740281760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fg5eo991_somendra-tomar-relative-fight_625x300_23_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmeerut-news%2Fon-camera-up-minister-somendra-tomar-relative-flower-vendors-exchange-blows-in-meeruts-narrow-road-7773618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fight%20broke%20out%20when%20Somendra%20Tomar's%20nephew%20was%20travelling%20in%20his%20Mahindra%20Scorpio%20on%20a%20jam-packed%20narrow%20road%2C%20which%20housed%20many%20flower%20shops%2C%20in%20Meerut.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmeerut-news%2Fon-camera-up-minister-somendra-tomar-relative-flower-vendors-exchange-blows-in-meeruts-narrow-road-7773618%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Champions%20Trophy%20Could%20Decide%20Rohit%20%26amp%3B%20Virat's%20ODI%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClass%20is%20permanent%2C%20form%20is%20temporary%26quot%3B.%20It's%20high%20time%20the%20adage%20comes%20with%20a%20rider%20in%20cricket%3A%20%E2%80%98subject%20to%20age%20of%20the%20athlete%20and%20how%20long%20he%2Fshe%20has%20been%20largely%20out%20of%20form'.%20At%20a%20certain%20point%20in%20time%2C%20almost%20every%20athlete%2C%20regardless%20of%20stature%20and%20class%2C%20races%20against%20time%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20mix.%20Some%20manage%20to%20beat%20the%20clock%2C%20most%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalling%20A%20Spade%20A%20Spade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20adage%20is%20being%20used%20by%20many%20to%20sum%20up%20where%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20pillars%20of%20modern-day%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20stand%20currently%2C%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20their%20ODI%20careers.%20With%20the%202025%20edition%20of%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20getting%20underway%2C%20the%20chorus%20of%20voices%20talking%20about%20these%20two%20stalwarts%20and%20what%20their%20ODI%20future%20might%20look%20like%20has%20reached%20a%20crescendo.%20And%20while%20many%20of%20the%20voices%20in%20that%20chorus%20are%20citing%20the%20above%20oft-used%20adage%2C%20not%20too%20many%20are%20calling%20the%20proverbial%20spade%20a%20spade%3A%20if%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20don't%20play%20tournament-defining%20knocks%20to%20significantly%20try%20and%20carry%20the%20team%20towards%20the%20title%2C%20their%20ODI%20days%20will%20be%20numbered.%20One%20match%20into%20India's%20campaign%20and%20the%20two%2C%20who%20looked%20good%20while%20they%20were%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20The%20Strongest%20Team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20really%20a%20secret%20that%20every%20national%20board%20and%20team%20management%20aims%20at%20building%20the%20strongest%20team%20possible%20with%20the%20next%20big%20tournament%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%20a%20World%20Cup%2C%20as%20the%20target.%20The%20build-up%20period%20was%20usually%20around%20two%20and%20half%20years%20at%20one%20time%2C%20with%20a%20certain%20fixed%20number%20of%20matches%20in%20mind%20where%20the%20team%20combination%20the%20management%20thinks%20will%20work%20best%20is%20tried%20out.%20Things%20changed%20somewhat%20of%20course%20after%20T20s%20became%20all%20the%20rage.%20Now%20that%20we%20have%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20every%20two%20years%2C%20that%20stock-taking%20and%20preparation%20period%20has%20shortened%20for%20the%20shortest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20ODIs%20though%2C%20it%20still%20remains%20at%20around%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20about%2020-30%20games.%20The%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20also%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%98mini-World%20Cup'%2C%20is%20being%20played%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202017%20and%20the%20next%20global%20ODI%20tournament%20will%20be%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%202027%2C%20roughly%20scheduled%20for%20October-November.%20That%20is%20over%20two%20years%20away.%20Realistically%2C%20players%20who%20are%20not%20demonstrating%20consistency%20are%20kept%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20long-term%20preparation%2C%20after%20being%20given%20an%20appropriate%20number%20of%20chances%2C%20as%20determined%20by%20the%20selectors%20and%20team%20management%20of%20the%20time.%20If%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20don't%20have%20a%20good%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20what%20are%20the%20chances%20they%20will%20still%20be%20in%20the%20reckoning%20for%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup%3F%20It's%20not%20really%20a%20tough%20question%20to%20answer%2C%20is%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20Superstars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20player%20wants%20to%20go%20out%20on%20his%20or%20her%20own%20terms%2C%20especially%20champion%20players.%20The%20last%20thing%20they%20want%20is%20to%20be%20pushed%20out.%20It%20wasn't%20surprising%20to%20see%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20retire%20from%20T20is%20right%20after%20India%20won%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20It%20was%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20bid%20adieu%20to%20the%20format%E2%80%94on%20the%20biggest%20of%20highs%20possible%E2%80%94as%20world%20champions.%20I%20believe%20both%20players%20might%20just%20have%20done%20the%20same%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%2C%20if%20India%20had%20won%20the%202023%20World%20Cup.%20But%20when%20the%20team%20faltered%20at%20the%20final%20hurdle%2C%20they%20must%20have%20felt%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20ending%20they%20want%20for%20their%20ODI%20legacies.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20is%20a%20format%20that%20has%20played%20the%20biggest%20role%20in%20making%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20who%20they%20are%3A%20global%20superstars.%20Rohit%20still%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20ODI%20double%20tons%20(3)%2C%20while%20Virat%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20the%20most%20ODI%20centuries%20(50)%20and%20is%20the%20player%20who%20re-defined%20ODI%20chases.%20Both%20players%20would%20want%20to%20exit%20the%20format%20on%20a%20high.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20best%20possible%20scenario%20right%20now%20would%20be%20that%20India%20clinches%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20title%2C%20with%20both%20star%20batters%20playing%20stellar%20knocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20unfold%20is%20players%20who%20are%20a%20few%20notches%20above%20the%20rest%20in%20talent%20and%20calibre%20use%20the%20biggest%20of%20platforms%20to%20roar%20back%20to%20life%20after%20being%20somewhat%20comatose.%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20earlier%20said%20that%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20%E2%80%9Chave%20got%20to%20play%20a%20massive%20role%E2%80%9D%20in%20India's%20Champions%20Trophy%20campaign%20this%20time.%20That%20statement%20might%20have%20been%20based%20on%20two%20things.%20One%2C%20the%20coach's%20overall%20faith%20in%20the%20latent%20talent%20and%20calibre%20of%20these%20two%20players.%20And%20two%2C%20just%20how%20effective%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20have%20traditionally%20been%20in%20ICC%20tournaments.%20A%20quick%20look%20at%20the%20statistics%20tells%20us%20that%20in%20the%20all-time%20list%20of%20most%20runs%20scored%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20combined%2C%20Virat%20sits%20at%20number%20two%2C%20behind%20only%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20with%20five%20centuries%20and%20an%20average%20of%20almost%2064%2C%20while%20Rohit%20is%20at%20number%20five%2C%20behind%20Kumar%20Sangakkara%2C%20with%20eight%20centuries%20and%20averaging%2058%20(till%20after%20the%20India%20vs%20Bangladesh%20match%20at%20the%20ongoing%20CT).%20History%20tells%20us%20that%20these%20two%20batting%20heroes%2C%20just%20like%20most%20batting%20legends%2C%20really%20come%20good%20on%20the%20biggest%20platforms%20of%20them%20all.%20Remember%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%3F%20Rohit%20crossed%20the%20fifty-run%20mark%20six%20times%20in%20nine%20innings%20and%20notched%20up%20hundreds%20five%20times.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20how%20much%20of%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20does%20still%20exist%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20man%20captaining%20the%20team%20in%20Dubai%20right%20now%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20Milestones%2C%20Team%20Glory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20and%20Virat%20have%20always%20been%20team-players%2C%20not%20focused%20on%20personal%20glory%20or%20statistics.%20In%20fact%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20first%20match%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20(the%20team)%20will%20not%20be%20looking%20at%20individual%20milestones.%E2%80%9D%20While%20that%20is%20true%2C%20to%20assume%20that%20neither%20player%20will%20be%20feeling%20any%20pressure%20at%20all%20to%20contribute%20big%20time%20for%20the%20team%20this%20time%20would%20also%20be%20na%C3%AFve.%20Despite%20outward%20appearances%2C%20both%20players%20will%20know%20that%20as%20the%20two%20most%20senior%20batters%20in%20the%20team%2C%20they%20have%20to%20score%2C%20and%20score%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20is%20exceptionally%20fit%20physically%20and%20mentally.%20Rohit%20is%20hands-down%20one%20of%20the%20best%20natural%20talents%20to%20have%20ever%20played%20international%20cricket.%20But%20is%20it%20these%20very%20characteristics%20that%20are%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20them%20making%20the%20subtle%20changes%20they%20need%20to%20make%20to%20their%20approach%2C%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20their%20careers%3F%20I%20spoke%20to%20Mumbai%20cricket%20legend%20Mr.%20Milind%20Rege%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20he%20tragically%20passed%20away%20at%20the%20age%20of%2076.%20Mr.%20Rege%2C%20a%20former%20Mumbai%20chief%20selector%20who%20lived%20and%20breathed%20Mumbai%20and%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20told%20me%20that%20he%20feels%20that%20since%20Virat%20is%20so%20fit%2C%20he%20hasn't%20thought%20about%20which%20shots%20he%20needs%20to%20cut%20out%20of%20his%20repertoire%2C%20like%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20did%20in%20the%20latter%20part%20of%20his%20career.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20day%20he%20(Virat)%20realises%20that%20%E2%80%98maybe%20I%20can%20play%20a%20little%20more%20percentage%20cricket'%2C%20he%20will%20start%20batting%20better.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20a%20Champions%20Trophy%20(title)%20win%20would%20hasten%20his%20(Virat's)%20decision%20to%20quit%20ODI%20cricket%20also%20and%20concentrate%20on%20Test%20cricket.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20Rohit%20is%20concerned%2C%20Mr.%20Rege%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdefinitely%20Rohit%20will%20have%20to%20work%20on%20his%20technique.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Rohit%20became%20the%20second-fastest%20batsman%20to%20reach%2011%2C000%20ODI%20runs.%20The%20fastest%20on%20that%20list%20is%20a%20certain%20Virat%20Kohli.%20Regardless%20of%20when%20these%20two%20legends%20of%20the%20game%20ride%20into%20the%20ODI%20sunset%2C%20let's%20hope%20they%20manage%20to%20do%20it%20on%20a%20big%20high%3A%20both%20for%20themselves%20and%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740281760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8bnni5p_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-x_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frohit-virats-odi-future-could-be-determined-in-this-champions-trophy-7773700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Thursday%2C%20Rohit%20became%20the%20second-fastest%20batsman%20to%20reach%2011%2C000%20ODI%20runs.%20The%20fastest%20on%20that%20list%20is%20a%20certain%20Virat%20Kohli.%20Regardless%20of%20when%20these%20two%20legends%20of%20the%20game%20ride%20into%20the%20ODI%20sunset%2C%20lets%20hope%20they%20manage%20to%20do%20it%20on%20a%20big%20hi