Fc4g05gzvp57o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g05gzvp57o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g05gzvp57o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20Fort%20Knox%20Gold%20Reserves%20And%20How%20Safe%20It%20Is%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20says%20Elon%20Musk%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20Fort%20Knox%2C%20the%20legendary%20depository%20in%20Kentucky%20for%20American%20gold%20reserves%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20gold%20is%20still%20there.%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20says%20there%20is%20an%20audit%20every%20year%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20gold%20is%20present%20and%20accounted%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20Bullion%20Depository%20at%20Fort%20Knox%20has%20stored%20precious%20metal%20bullion%20reserves%20for%20the%20United%20States%20since%201937%20and%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20security%20and%20well-protected.%20Along%20with%20protecting%20gold%20reserves%2C%20Fort%20Knox%20is%20currently%20also%20used%20as%20the%20Army's%20human%20resources%20command%20center%2C%20and%20it%20hosts%20the%20Army's%20largest%20annual%20training%20event%20each%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20open%20up%20the%20doors.%20We're%20going%20to%20inspect%20Fort%20Knox%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20to%20Republican%20governors%20Thursday%20evening.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20open%20it%20and%20the%20cupboards%20are%20bare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFort%20Knox%20history%20and%20location%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20post%20is%20about%2035%20miles%20south%20of%20Louisville%20and%20encompasses%20109%2C000%20acres%20in%20three%20Kentucky%20counties%20-%20Bullitt%2C%20Hardin%2C%20and%20Mead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECamp%20Knox%20was%20established%20during%20World%20War%20I%20and%20became%20an%20artillery%20training%20center%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Army%20post's%20website.%20It%20was%20made%20a%20permanent%20installation%20in%201932%20and%20has%20been%20known%20since%20then%20as%20Fort%20Knox.%20The%20first%20gold%20arrived%20at%20Fort%20Knox%20in%201937%20with%20the%201st%20Cavalry%20Regiment%20called%20on%20to%20guard%20the%20shipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-banks-are-flying-gold-worth-billions-of-dollars-from-london-to-new-york-heres-why-7731024%5C%22%3EWhy%C2%A0US%20Banks%20Are%20Flying%20Gold%20Worth%20Billions%20Of%20Dollars%20From%20London%20To%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20outbreak%20of%20World%20War%20II%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20Army%20created%20the%20Armored%20Force%20at%20Fort%20Knox%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20soldiers%20were%20ordered%20there%20and%20introduced%20to%20the%20tank.%20For%20nearly%2080%20years%2C%20the%20post%20was%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BHome%20of%20Cavalry%20and%20Armor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20the%20Army%20decided%20to%20move%20the%20Armor%20Center%20and%20School%20to%20Fort%20Benning%2C%20Georgia%2C%20and%20the%20Human%20Resource%20Command%20Center%20of%20Excellence%20was%20established%20at%20Fort%20Knox.%20In%202013%2C%20ROTC%20Cadet%20Summer%20Training%20was%20consolidated%20at%20Fort%20Knox.%20The%20post%20hosts%20the%20Army's%20largest%20annual%20training%20event%20each%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20gold%20is%20stored%20at%20Fort%20Knox%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Mint%2C%20current%20gold%20holdings%20at%20the%20US%20Bullion%20Depository%20at%20Fort%20Knox%20are%20147.3%20million%20ounces.%20About%20half%20of%20the%20Treasury's%20stored%20gold%20is%20kept%20at%20Fort%20Knox.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20gold%20ever%20been%20removed%3F%20The%20Mint%20says%20only%20very%20small%20quantities%20have%20been%20removed%20to%20test%20the%20purity%20of%20the%20gold%20during%20regularly%20scheduled%20audits.%20Except%20for%20these%20samples%2C%20no%20gold%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20or%20from%20the%20depository%20for%20many%20years.%20The%20gold's%20book%20value%20is%20%2442.22%20per%20ounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20how%20secure%20is%20Fort%20Knox%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20depository%20is%20very%20secure.%20The%20actual%20structure%20and%20content%20of%20the%20facility%20is%20known%20by%20only%20a%20few%2C%20and%20no%20one%20person%20knows%20all%20the%20procedures%20to%20open%20the%20vault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20known%20publicly%20is%20that%20the%20facility%20was%20built%20in%201936%20using%2016%2C000%20cubic%20feet%20of%20granite%2C%204%2C200%20cubic%20yards%20of%20concrete%2C%20750%20tons%20of%20reinforcing%20steel%20and%20670%20tons%20of%20structural%20steel.%20The%20facility%20is%20heavily%20guarded%20and%20has%20broken%20its%20strict%20policy%20of%20not%20allowing%20visitors%20only%20three%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHas%20anyone%20been%20allowed%20to%20see%20the%20gold%20reserves%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201974%2C%20the%20US%20Mint%20opened%20the%20vaults%20to%20a%20group%20of%20journalists%20and%20a%20congressional%20delegation%20so%20they%20could%20see%20the%20gold%20reserves.%20The%20Treasury%20secretary%20allowed%20the%20visit%20after%20persistent%20rumours%20that%20the%20gold%20had%20been%20removed.%20Until%20then%2C%20the%20only%20person%20other%20than%20authorised%20personnel%20to%20access%20the%20vaults%20was%20President%20Franklin%20D%20Roosevelt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20vaults%20have%20been%20opened%20one%20other%20time%3A%20In%202017%2C%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Steve%20Mnuchin%20visited%20with%20Kentucky%20Gov.%20Matt%20Bevin%20and%20congressional%20representatives.%20Current%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20has%20said%20he%20would%20happily%20arran