tronger%20than%20the%20occupier%2C%20God%20willing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20city%20of%20Ramallah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'blatant%20violation'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Prisoners'%20Club%20advocacy%20group%20had%20said%20Israel%20would%20free%20620%20inmates%20on%20Saturday%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Gazans%20taken%20into%20custody%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Netanyahu's%20announcement%2C%20Hamas%20spokesperson%20Abdel%20Latif%20al-Qanou%20said%20Israel's%20%26quot%3Bfailure%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20release...%20at%20the%20agreed-upon%20time%20constitutes%20a%20blatant%20violation%20of%20the%20agreement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQanou%20called%20on%20the%20truce%20mediators%20to%20pressure%20Israel%20to%20%26quot%3Bimplement%20its%20provisions%20without%20delay%20or%20obstruction%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delayed%20release%20comes%20after%20an%20emotional%20few%20days%20in%20Israel%2C%20where%20the%20remains%20of%20hostage%20Shiri%20Bibas%20were%20identified%20after%20the%20initial%20handover%20of%20a%20different%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-hostage-kisses-forehead-of-hamas-members-7769507%5C%22%3EFreed%20Israeli%20Hostage%20Kisses%20Forehead%20Of%20Hamas%20Operatives%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20said%20Hamas%20will%20pay%20%26quot%3Bthe%20full%20price%26quot%3B%20for%20what%20he%20termed%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20truce%20deal%20over%20Bibas's%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBibas%20and%20her%20two%20young%20sons%2C%20among%20dozens%20taken%20captive%20during%20Hamas's%20October%207%2C%202023%20attack%20on%20Israel%20that%20triggered%20the%20war%2C%20had%20become%20symbols%20of%20the%20ordeal%20suffered%20by%20the%20Israeli%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForensics%20expert%20Chen%20Kugel%20said%20an%20autopsy%20conducted%20on%20their%20remains%20found%20%26quot%3Bno%20evidence%20of%20injuries%20caused%20by%20a%20bombing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20had%20claimed%20that%20all%20three%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20air%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Coming%20back%20home'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20Israelis%20released%20Saturday%20were%20the%20last%20group%20of%20living%20hostages%20set%20to%20be%20freed%20under%20the%20truce's%20first%20phase.%20The%20deal%2C%20which%20has%20so%20far%20enabled%20the%20release%20of%2030%20captives%2C%20is%20due%20to%20expire%20in%20early%20March.%20Negotiations%20for%20a%20second%20phase%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20lead%20to%20a%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20war%2C%20have%20yet%20to%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20ceremony%20in%20Nuseirat%2C%20central%20Gaza%2C%20Eliya%20Cohen%2C%2027%2C%20Omer%20Shem%20Tov%2C%2022%2C%20and%20Israeli-Argentine%20Omer%20Wenkert%2C%2023%2C%20waved%20from%20a%20stage%2C%20flanked%20by%20masked%20Hamas%20operatives%2C%20before%20their%20handover%20to%20the%20Red%20Cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20the%20look%20on%20his%20face%2C%20he's%20calm%2C%20he%20knows%20he's%20coming%20back%20home...%20He's%20a%20real%20hero%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wenkert's%20friend%20Rory%20Grosz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20cold%20winter%20rain%20in%20Rafah%2C%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20operatives%20handed%20over%20Tal%20Shoham%2C%2040%2C%20and%20Avera%20Mengistu%2C%2038%2C%20who%20both%20appeared%20dazed.%20A%20sixth%20hostage%2C%20Hisham%20al-Sayed%2C%2037%2C%20was%20later%20released%20in%20private%20and%20taken%20back%20to%20Israeli%20territory%2C%20the%20military%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayed%2C%20a%20Bedouin%20Muslim%2C%20and%20Mengistu%2C%20an%20Ethiopian%20Jew%2C%20had%20been%20held%20in%20Gaza%20for%20about%20a%20decade%20after%20they%20entered%20the%20territory%20individually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayed's%20family%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20long-awaited%20moment%2