E%20to%20be%20with%20my%20long-distance%20boyfriend%2C%20who's%20now%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlthough%20my%20friends%20were%20jealous%20I%20was%20moving%20to%20a%20sunny%20%26quot%3Bparadise%2C%26quot%3B%20San%20Diego%20wasn't%20for%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20found%20the%20weather%20to%20be%20boring%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20like%20how%20hard%20it%20was%20to%20get%20around%20without%20a%20car.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-philadelphia-to-chicago-surprising-things-cons-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Chicago%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20six%20years%2C%20I%20had%20a%20fulfilling%20career%2C%20great%20friends%2C%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20several%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would've%20happily%20stayed%20there%20forever%2C%20but%20my%20then-boyfriend%20(now%20husband)%20was%20in%20the%20Navy.%20We'd%20been%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-distance-fiance-relationship-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20where%20he%20was%20currently%20located%3A%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20my%20Midwest%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20about%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-charming-town-northern-california-hated-it-grass-valley-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20of%20their%20eyes%20would%20grow%20wide%20with%20envy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20some%20who'd%20never%20been%20to%20San%20Diego%20%E2%80%94%20would%20tell%20me%20how%20lucky%20I%20was%20to%20move%20to%20a%20sunny%20%26quot%3Bparadise%26quot%3B%20with%20so%20many%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20smile%20and%20nod%2C%20but%20I%20was%20actually%20very%20reluctant%20to