he%20bright%20side%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20San%20Diego's%20public%20transportation.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20coming%20from%20Chicago%20%E2%80%94%20a%20big%20city%20with%20extensive%20bus%20and%20train%20options%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20very%20low%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20take%20public%20transit%2C%20it%20sometimes%20took%20me%20an%20hour%20or%20more%20and%20several%20connections%20to%20travel%20throughout%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20accepted%20that%20San%20Diego%20and%20I%20just%20don't%20have%20compatible%20priorities%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20getting%20around.%20Living%20here%20reminded%20me%20how%20much%20I%20prefer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-walkable-cities-for-pedestrians-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalkable%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20car-centric%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff374f0d-060e-496b-90d9-05a08d4af668%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESometimes%20it%20was%20even%20hard%20to%20enjoy%20the%20beaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22La%20Jolla%20Shores%20beach%20and%20Scripps%20Pier%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20California%2C%20and%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793e2c32fcded5e9074a54c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Diego%20is%20beautiful%2C%20but%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20watch%20people%20litter%20and%20leave%20trash%20on%20its%20beaches.%3Cp%3EL.%20Toshio%20Kishiyama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20my%20Midwestern%20friends%20were%20jealous%20of%20just%20how%20many%20beautiful%20local%20beaches%20I'd%20have%20access%20to%20in%20San%20Diego.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20these%20beaches%20also%20drew%20in%20many%20tourists%20and%20visitors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20didn't%20always%20know%20if